VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (^|\s|=\s?)eval\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(input\(|request|params|query|user_input|base64|pickle) && MISSING:(allowlist|whitelist)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects instances of eval() that can lead to command injection vulnerabilities if used with untrusted input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Command Injection: eval().
